snippet.title: Gangs of Sherwood - Gameplay Overview | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Fight the armies of the Sheriff of Nottingham and lead the rebellion, solo or in co-op with up to 4 players in Gangs of Sherwood.

Gangs of Sherwood will be available on November 2nd 2023 on Playstation 5.
